nodes.text: Nigel Timothy Godrich (born August 1, 1971) is an English record producer, record engineer and musician who portrays FN-9330 in the 2015 film Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens and FN-2802 in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker. He is known for his work with the band Radiohead.

Gorich landed the role as FN-9330 in The Force Awakens with the help of British filmmaker Edgar Wright. Although Godrich played FN-2802 in The Rise of Skywalker, the character was voiced by David W. Collins.
